The paper focuses on the Visual Dialog Challenge, which involves understanding and generating natural language descriptions of images. This suggests that the paper is likely to be related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of discriminative models also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). Finally, the use of NDCG and MRR metrics suggests a focus on information retrieval (cs.IR).
